    </p>
</div>

<!-- ─── Step 4 ───────────────────────────────────────────── -->

<div style="margin-bottom: 24px; padding: 20px; background: #fff; border: 1px solid #ddd; border-radius: 6px;">
    <h3 style="margin-top: 0; color: #6a1b9a;">
        <span style="display: inline-block; width: 32px; height: 32px; line-height: 32px; text-align: center; background: #6a1b9a; color: #fff; border-radius: 50%; font-size: 16px; margin-right: 10px;">4</span>
        Deploy Your Application
    </h3>
    <p style="font-size: 14px; line-height: 1.7;">
        Go to the <strong>Deploy</strong> tab and click <strong>"Deploy Now"</strong>. Here's what happens behind the scenes:
    </p>
    <ol style="font-size: 14px; line-height: 2.2;">
        <li>Your code is downloaded from the repository into a new, timestamped folder</li>
        <li>PHP dependencies are installed (Composer)</li>
